Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:27.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}没有泪水的明天过后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:31.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}会有温柔的未来等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:37.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:41.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:45.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只属于自己的答案
